{"id":3400,"date":"2024-05-04T14:42:36","date_gmt":"2024-05-04T07:42:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=3400"},"modified":"2024-05-04T15:13:15","modified_gmt":"2024-05-04T08:13:15","slug":"kham-pha-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-tuyet-tac-kien-truc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/kham-pha-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-tuyet-tac-kien-truc\/","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u &#8211; Tuy\u1ec7t t\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng n\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em><strong>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong>, c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 S\u01a1n L\u0103ng, t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i n\u00fai Sam, TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Nam B\u1ed9. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch b\u1edfi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa n\u00e9t truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang th\u1eafc m\u1eafc du l\u1ecbch An Giang n\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u th\u00ec b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua khi du l\u1ecbch An Giang.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-an-giang.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-an-giang.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch \u1edf an giang\" class=\"wp-image-3401\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-an-giang.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-an-giang-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u An Giang<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-ultimate-post-table-of-content aligncenter ultp-block-ead8aa\"><div class=\"ultp-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"ultp-block-toc\"><div class=\"ultp-toc-header\"><div class=\"ultp-toc-heading\">Table of Contents<\/div><div class=\"ultp-collapsible-toggle  ultp-collapsible-right\"><a class=\"ultp-collapsible-text ultp-collapsible-open\" href=\"javascript:;\">[Open]<\/a><a class=\"ultp-collapsible-text ultp-collapsible-hide\" href=\"javascript:;\">[Close]<\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ultp-block-toc-style1 ultp-block-toc-body\" style=\"display:block;\"><ul class=\"ultp-toc-lists\"><li><a href=\"#_Gi\u1edbi_thi\u1ec7u_v\u1ec1_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">1. Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><ul class=\"ultp-toc-lists\"><li><a href=\"#_V\u1ecb_tr\u00ed_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">1.1 V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_N\u00e9t_\u0111\u1ed9c_\u0111\u00e1o_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">1.2 N\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><a href=\"#_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u_v\u1edbi_l\u1ecbch_s\u1eed_v\u00e0_ki\u1ebfn_tr\u00fac_\u0111\u1ed9c_\u0111\u00e1o\">2. L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/a><ul class=\"ultp-toc-lists\"><li><a href=\"#_Ti\u1ec3u_s\u1eed_v\u00e0_c\u00f4ng_tr\u1ea1ng_c\u1ee7a_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u:\">2.1 Ti\u1ec3u s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u:<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_Qu\u00e1_tr\u00ecnh_x\u00e2y_d\u1ef1ng_v\u00e0_gi\u00e1_tr\u1ecb_l\u1ecbch_s\u1eed_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">2.2 Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_Ki\u1ebfn_tr\u00fac_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">2.3 Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><ul class=\"ultp-toc-lists\"><li><a href=\"#_Khu\u00f4n_vi\u00ean_l\u0103ng\">2.3.1 Khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean l\u0103ng<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_C\u1ed5ng_Tam_Quan\">2.3.2 C\u1ed5ng Tam Quan<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_\u0110\u1ec1n_th\u1edd_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7unbsp;\">2.3.3 \u0110\u1ec1n th\u1edd Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_\u00dd_ngh\u0129a_v\u00e0_gi\u00e1_tr\u1ecb_v\u0103n_h\u00f3a_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">2.3.4 \u00dd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><a href=\"#_H\u01b0\u1edbng_d\u1eabn_tham_quan_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">3. H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><ul class=\"ultp-toc-lists\"><li><a href=\"#_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u_v\u00e0_C\u00e1p_treo_n\u00fai_Sam\">3.1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_C\u00e1ch_di_chuy\u1ec3n_\u0111\u1ebfn_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\">3.2 C\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_Gi\u00e1_v\u00e9_tham_quan_v\u00e0_th\u1eddi_gian_m\u1edf_c\u1eeda:\">3.3 Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 tham quan v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian m\u1edf c\u1eeda:<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#_Nh\u1eefng_l\u01b0u_\u00fd_khi_tham_quan_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u:\">3.4 Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><a href=\"#_K\u1ebft_lu\u1eadn:\">4. K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Gi\u1edbi_thi\u1ec7u_v\u1ec1_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>1. Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_V\u1ecb_tr\u00ed_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>1.1 V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai Sam h\u00f9ng v\u0129, c\u00e1ch trung t\u00e2m TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c kho\u1ea3ng 5km. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1873 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1edd c\u00fang Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u &#8211; v\u1ecb quan t\u00e0i ba l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c khai hoang, m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng S\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long. L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i An Giang, thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-toa-lac-tai-nui-sam-an-giang.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-toa-lac-tai-nui-sam-an-giang.jpg\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y 1 ng\u00e0y n\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u\" class=\"wp-image-3403\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-toa-lac-tai-nui-sam-an-giang.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-toa-lac-tai-nui-sam-an-giang-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i n\u00fai Sam, An Giang<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_N\u00e9t_\u0111\u1ed9c_\u0111\u00e1o_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>1.2 N\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c di t\u00edch kh\u00e1c, khi\u1ebfn n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua khi du l\u1ecbch An Giang. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo phong c\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho L\u0103ng. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed tr\u00ean l\u0103ng m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea1m tr\u1ed5 tinh x\u1ea3o, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i hoa v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee3 x\u01b0a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady, ngo\u00e0i ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, L\u0103ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba. N\u1eb1m tr\u00ean ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai Sam h\u00f9ng v\u0129, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p, bao qu\u00e1t to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh. Du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba tham quan l\u0103ng m\u1ed9, v\u1eeba ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh, thanh m\u00e1t.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/lh7-us.googleusercontent.com\/yGqFenASWg7_lwT-tK7RVvfjtZgXUPHZVlShVV1a2tqZ9MiU4WqZGBE9F7d4FhQyxJC_pFHj94pbgUwH1t2sGx0Oda9uWs8MtRYlXrBKJdmzpHJ8o776QLvK2vM_02xqrX2dnB97m_bWCjdHksJtEvQ\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y\" title=\"\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>N\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u01b0u gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u &#8211; v\u1ecb anh h\u00f9ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c khai hoang, m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng S\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long. Du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham quan l\u0103ng m\u1ed9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u_v\u1edbi_l\u1ecbch_s\u1eed_v\u00e0_ki\u1ebfn_tr\u00fac_\u0111\u1ed9c_\u0111\u00e1o\"><strong>2. L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Ti\u1ec3u_s\u1eed_v\u00e0_c\u00f4ng_tr\u1ea1ng_c\u1ee7a_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u:\"><strong>2.1 Ti\u1ec3u s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u:<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u (1804 &#8211; 1886) t\u00ean th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb quan t\u00e0i ba l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u vua T\u1ef1 \u0110\u1ee9c. \u00d4ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c khai hoang, m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng S\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long. Nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n t\u00f4n vinh l\u00e0 &#8220;\u0110\u1ee9c Tho\u1ea1i&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/tuong-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpeg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/tuong-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpeg\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y\" class=\"wp-image-3405\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/tuong-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpeg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/tuong-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-600x449.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>T\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00d4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Qu\u00e1_tr\u00ecnh_x\u00e2y_d\u1ef1ng_v\u00e0_gi\u00e1_tr\u1ecb_l\u1ecbch_s\u1eed_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>2.2 Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1873, sau khi \u00f4ng qua \u0111\u1eddi. L\u0103ng m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo phong c\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n k\u00ednh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u. L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 tri \u00e2n v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n An Giang \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb anh h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng khai hoang, m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/noi-tho-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/noi-tho-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\" alt=\"N\u01a1i th\u1edd \u00d4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u\" class=\"wp-image-3406\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/noi-tho-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/noi-tho-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>N\u01a1i th\u1edd \u00d4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Ki\u1ebfn_tr\u00fac_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>2.3 Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Khu\u00f4n_vi\u00ean_l\u0103ng\"><strong>2.3.1 Khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean l\u0103ng<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn L\u0103ng, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 m\u00e1t m\u1ebb trong l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 an y\u00ean t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y xanh c\u1ed5 th\u1ee5 bao quanh l\u0103ng. D\u1ea1o b\u01b0\u1edbc trong kh\u00f4ng gian an y\u00ean, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng giai tho\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khuon-vien-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khuon-vien-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch an giang n\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u\" class=\"wp-image-3407\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khuon-vien-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khuon-vien-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_C\u1ed5ng_Tam_Quan\"><strong>2.3.2 C\u1ed5ng Tam Quan<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ed1i v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 C\u1ed5ng Tam Quan. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y l\u00e0 do l\u1ed1i v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 3 c\u1ed5ng h\u00ecnh b\u00e1n nguy\u1ec7t, 3 c\u1ed5ng n\u00e0y l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho tam quan ch\u00ednh l\u00e0: Thi\u00ean &#8211; \u0110\u1ecba &#8211; Nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cong-tam-quan-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cong-tam-quan-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg\" alt=\"kinh nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y\" class=\"wp-image-3408\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cong-tam-quan-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cong-tam-quan-tai-lang-thoai-ngoc-hau-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>C\u1ed5ng Tam Quan t\u1ea1i L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i c\u1ed5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng g\u1ea1ch nung, c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao kho\u1ea3ng 4m v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng 6m. Ph\u00eda tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh c\u1ed5ng c\u00f3 m\u00e1i ng\u00f3i cong cong v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea1m kh\u1eafc hoa v\u0103n r\u1ed3ng ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng uy nghi\u00eam.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_\u0110\u1ec1n_th\u1edd_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7unbsp;\"><strong>2.3.3 \u0110\u1ec1n th\u1edd Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c b\u00ean trong l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ec1n th\u1edd \u00f4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ec1n th\u1edd g\u1ed3m 3 gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3p ng\u00f3i \u00e2m d\u01b0\u01a1ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9. Gian ch\u00ednh th\u1edd \u00f4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, hai gian b\u00ean th\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n linh. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t trang nghi\u00eam v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00f4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u uy nghi \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean b\u1ec7 th\u1edd cao.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n n\u1eb1m trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i an ngh\u1ec9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a danh th\u1ea7n Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u (1761 &#8211; 1829), v\u1ecb quan t\u00e0i ba c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc b\u1edfi b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh ki\u00ean c\u1ed1, cao kho\u1ea3ng 2m, d\u00e0y kho\u1ea3ng 0,5m. B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u1eb1ng g\u1ea1ch nung v\u00e0 tr\u00e1t v\u00f4i v\u1eefa, c\u00f3 m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng r\u00eau phong, mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9 Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u n\u1eb1m ch\u00ednh gi\u1eefa khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1 xanh nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i, cao kho\u1ea3ng 1m, r\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng 2m. M\u1ed9 c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt, m\u00e1i cong cong, tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t l\u01b0 h\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u00ean tr\u00e1i m\u1ed9 Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ea5t Ch\u00e2u Th\u1ecb T\u1ebf, b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00e0 th\u1ee9 th\u1ea5t Di\u1ec7c ph\u1ea9m phu nh\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Mi\u1ec7t. Hai m\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n m\u1ed9 Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, c\u0169ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1 xanh nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i. Ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t bia \u0111\u00e1 ghi ch\u00e9p ti\u1ec3u s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c phu nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khu-mo-phan-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-va-vo.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khu-mo-phan-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-va-vo.jpg\" alt=\"du l\u1ecbch an giang c\u00f3 g\u00ec\" class=\"wp-image-3409\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khu-mo-phan-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-va-vo.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/khu-mo-phan-ong-thoai-ngoc-hau-va-vo-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Khu m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n \u00d4ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 v\u1ee3<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_\u00dd_ngh\u0129a_v\u00e0_gi\u00e1_tr\u1ecb_v\u0103n_h\u00f3a_c\u1ee7a_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>2.3.4 \u00dd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c gia, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ghi d\u1ea5u nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3n h\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c khai ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n An Giang, L\u0103ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng khai ph\u00e1 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n An Giang, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn tham quan du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i, thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng khai ph\u00e1 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_H\u01b0\u1edbng_d\u1eabn_tham_quan_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>3. H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u_v\u00e0_C\u00e1p_treo_n\u00fai_Sam\"><strong>3.1 L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 KDL C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai, N\u00fai Sam, thu\u1ed9c ph\u01b0\u1eddng N\u00fai Sam, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hai \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00e1ch nhau kho\u1ea3ng 1,5km.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cap-treo-len-nui-sam-ngam-tron-chau-doc.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cap-treo-len-nui-sam-ngam-tron-chau-doc.jpg\" alt=\"khu du l\u1ecbch sinh th\u00e1i \u1edf an giang\" class=\"wp-image-3410\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cap-treo-len-nui-sam-ngam-tron-chau-doc.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cap-treo-len-nui-sam-ngam-tron-chau-doc-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>KDL C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><strong>KDL C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam<\/strong><\/p>\n<cite>C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i Khu Du l\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam, An Giang, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a du kh\u00e1ch l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n, m\u1edf ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft b\u1ea1n to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c l\u00e2n c\u1eadn. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a, ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 check in c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ngh\u0129 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.&nbsp;<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Xem ngay <a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/danh-thang\/\">M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i danh th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i KDL C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/kdl-cap-treo-nui-sam-ruc-ro-ve-dem.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/kdl-cap-treo-nui-sam-ruc-ro-ve-dem.jpg\" alt=\"khu du l\u1ecbch \u1edf an giang\" class=\"wp-image-3411\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/kdl-cap-treo-nui-sam-ruc-ro-ve-dem.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/kdl-cap-treo-nui-sam-ruc-ro-ve-dem-600x401.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>C\u00e1p treo l\u00ean n\u00fai Sam ng\u1eafm tr\u1ecdn Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch sau:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u0110i b\u1ed9: <\/strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u1ed9 theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f2n ho\u1eb7c b\u1eadc thang l\u00ean n\u00fai. Qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 d\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 15-20 ph\u00fat.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>\u0110i xe \u0111i\u1ec7n:<\/strong> Du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu\u00ea xe \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n l\u00ean n\u00fai. Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 20.000 &#8211; 30.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi\/l\u01b0\u1ee3t.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>\u0110i xe \u00f4m:<\/strong> \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t, tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111i b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c \u0111i xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/duong-xe-di-chuyen-len-nui-sam.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/duong-xe-di-chuyen-len-nui-sam.jpg\" alt=\"\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai sam\" class=\"wp-image-3412\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/duong-xe-di-chuyen-len-nui-sam.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/duong-xe-di-chuyen-len-nui-sam-600x356.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng xe di chuy\u1ec3n l\u00ean n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Du kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean mang theo gi\u00e0y d\u00e9p tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 m\u0169 n\u00f3n khi di chuy\u1ec3n l\u00ean n\u00fai.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>N\u00ean mang theo n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tham quan.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Du kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean gi\u1eef g\u00ecn v\u1ec7 sinh chung v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3 r\u00e1c b\u1eeba b\u00e3i tr\u00ean n\u00fai.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><strong>G\u1ee3i \u00fd du l\u1ecbch<\/strong><\/p>\n<cite><strong>Ngo\u00e0i ra, du kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam trong m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i.<\/strong> Du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c \u0111i xe \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u00ean tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, sau \u0111\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n qua KDL \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng C\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam, v\u1eeba ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, v\u1eeba ng\u1eafm c\u1ea3nh v\u1eadt t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao khi \u0111i c\u00e1p.&nbsp;<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_C\u00e1ch_di_chuy\u1ec3n_\u0111\u1ebfn_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u\"><strong>3.2 C\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>T\u1eeb Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: <\/strong>m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb TPHCM \u0111\u1ebfn An Giang tham quan c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ng\u00e0y nay, giao th\u00f4ng c\u0169ng thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Xe kh\u00e1ch:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e3ng xe uy t\u00edn nh\u01b0 Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Trang, Hu\u00ea Ki\u1ec1u, An Giang,&#8230; v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 120.000 &#8211; <strong>2<\/strong>50.000 VN\u0110\/l\u01b0\u1ee3t<strong> (t\u00f9y th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m). <\/strong>&nbsp;Th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3ng 5 &#8211; 6 ti\u1ebfng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Xe m\u00e1y\/\u00f4 t\u00f4:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;Qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i kho\u1ea3ng 200km, \u0111i theo Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 1A ho\u1eb7c Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 N2. Th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3ng 4 &#8211; 5 ti\u1ebfng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>T\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh l\u00e2n c\u1eadn:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng xe kh\u00e1ch, xe m\u00e1y, \u00f4 t\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c xe bu\u00fdt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y theo \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Gi\u00e1_v\u00e9_tham_quan_v\u00e0_th\u1eddi_gian_m\u1edf_c\u1eeda:\"><strong>3.3 Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 tham quan v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian m\u1edf c\u1eeda:<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9:<\/strong> Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Th\u1eddi gian m\u1edf c\u1eeda:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>L\u0103ng m\u1edf c\u1eeda t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y trong tu\u1ea7n.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gi\u1edd m\u1edf c\u1eeda: 7h00 &#8211; 18h00.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u g\u1ee3i \u00fd:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><strong>L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u g\u1ee3i \u00fd<\/strong><\/p>\n<cite><strong>Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng:<\/strong> <br>&#8211; Di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u.<br>&#8211; Tham quan C\u1ed5ng Tam Quan, B\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh phong.<br>&#8211; Vi\u1ebfng Mi\u1ebfu th\u1edd Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb quan t\u00e0i ba.<br>&#8211; Tham quan M\u1ed9 Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, b\u00e0y t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng khai ph\u00e1 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t.<br><strong>Bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u:<\/strong> <br>&#8211; D\u1ea1o b\u01b0\u1edbc trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean l\u0103ng, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 thanh b\u00ecnh.<br>&#8211; Tham quan c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0: nh\u00e0 bia, nh\u00e0 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea3nh, gi\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc,&#8230;<br>&#8211; Th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c qu\u00e1n \u0103n xung quanh l\u0103ng.<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_Nh\u1eefng_l\u01b0u_\u00fd_khi_tham_quan_L\u0103ng_Tho\u1ea1i_Ng\u1ecdc_H\u1ea7u:\"><strong>3.4 Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u:<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Du kh\u00e1ch khi \u0111\u1ebfn tham quan L\u0103ng, c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u sau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n k\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian t\u00f4n nghi\u00eam v\u00e0 an y\u00ean n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Trang ph\u1ee5c:<\/strong> \u0102n m\u1eb7c l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>H\u00e0nh vi:<\/strong> Gi\u1eef g\u00ecn v\u1ec7 sinh chung, kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3 r\u00e1c b\u1eeba b\u00e3i.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n:<\/strong> Gi\u1eef tr\u1eadt t\u1ef1, kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 to.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh:<\/strong> Xin ph\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang tham quan ho\u1eb7c c\u00fang b\u00e1i.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mua s\u1eafm:<\/strong> C\u1ea9n th\u1eadn khi mua s\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed3 l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m, so s\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Ngo\u00e0i ra, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i di\u1ec5n ra quanh n\u0103m t\u1ea1i L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 L\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i V\u00eda Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10 th\u00e1ng 5 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/du-khach-vieng-lang.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/du-khach-vieng-lang.jpg\" alt=\"tour du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y\" class=\"wp-image-3413\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/du-khach-vieng-lang.jpg 800w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/du-khach-vieng-lang-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Du kh\u00e1ch vi\u1ebfng L\u0103ng&nbsp;<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"_K\u1ebft_lu\u1eadn:\"><strong>4. K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c gia m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n An Giang. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho du kh\u00e1ch mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 h\u00f2a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean thanh b\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn tham quan L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Truy c\u1eadp m\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 <a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/tin-tuc\/\">c\u00e1c giai tho\u1ea1i, truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n<\/a> xoay quanh v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t linh thi\u00eang &#8211; An Giang nh\u00e9! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>KDL C\u00c1P TREO N\u00daI SAM<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Hotline: <\/strong><a href=\"tel:\"> 0869.519.678 &#8211; 0869.519.679<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Email:<\/strong> <a href=\"mailto:saletour.mga@gmail.com\">saletour.mga@gmail.com<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fanpage:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/captreonuisamchaudoc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/captreonuisam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">KDL C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i An Giang? Xem ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam s\u1ebd gi\u1